title: Chicken Invaders 2
description: The game is divided into 11 planets, each of which is made up by 10 waves. To advance through each wave, fire your spaceship guns at chickens to destroy them while avoiding falling eggs, asteroids, and other dangerous items. You can increase your spaceship&#039;s firepower as well as your chances of staying alive by collecting various bonuses that appear as chickens are killed. The game ends when you successfully complete all 110 waves (wee!), or you lose all your lives (boo!), whichever comes first. Good luck!
